Lackman shares the building with Shawnee Chamber of Commerce and is neighbors to ALDI and Chili’s Grill & Bar. data.text:
Lackman Branch is right off Shawnee Mission Parkway and Lackman Road. Lackman shares the building with Shawnee Chamber of Commerce and is neighbors to ALDI and Chili’s Grill & Bar. Lackman is across from Shawnee Station which hosts a range of shopping stores such as Target, Bed Bath & Beyond, Michaels, Kohl’s, OfficeMax, Starbucks, T-Mobile and PetSmart.

Our expert staff is ready to serve all of your personal banking, business banking, mortgage loans and commercial banking. Lackman is open on Saturdays from 9:00 am-12:00 pm and offers a 24-hour ATM.
